</code></pre><h2 id="customization">Customization</h2>
<p>Currently, <code>arscript-mode</code> provides a basic set of features optimized for general usage. Future versions may include customizable options based on user feedback.</p>
<h2 id="contributing">Contributing</h2>
<p>Contributions to <code>arscript-mode</code> are welcome! Whether it&rsquo;s bug reports, feature suggestions, or code contributions, feel free to reach out or submit pull requests on GitHub.</p>
